OL,3,CCommunity rallies to renovate a home
OL,4,Cwith profits funding new school
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,FA community is rallying together to
OL,8,Frenovate a house, with the profits
OL,9,Fgoing towards funding a new school
OL,10,Fplayground.
OL,12,FAn estate agent in Mountain Ash,
OL,13,FRhondda Cynon Taf, has teamed up with
OL,14,Ftradespeople and volunteers to
OL,15,Frenovate a home, to try and fund a new
OL,16,Fplayground for pupils at nearby
OL,17,FCaegarw Primary School.
