OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,FThe Playground Project has come about
OL,8,Fafter the school's playground
OL,9,Fequipment became too old to be used
OL,10,Fsafely, and was taken away.
OL,12,FThe school estimates it will cost
OL,13,F#50,000 to build a "safe and fun
OL,14,Fplayground" for its 160 pupils.
OL,16,FActing headteacher Nicola Richards
OL,17,Fsaid: "The children were absolutely
OL,18,Fdevastated, they were such big
OL,19,Fclimbing frames, you could easily have
OL,20,Fabout 20 children on there at a time."
