OL,3,CCommunity rallies to renovate a home
OL,4,Cwith profits funding new school
OL,5,Cplayground
OL,7,FChris Roberts, managing director of T
OL,8,FSamuel Estate Agents, said: "We've
OL,9,Fbeen inundated in fairness, local
OL,10,Fbusinesses all wanting to help, asking
OL,11,Fhow they can get involved.
OL,13,F"We've had some big companies reach
OL,14,Fout, which was fantastic.
OL,16,F"We're really excited to see it get
OL,17,Foff the ground and start rolling.
OL,19,F"It's a great community here, the
OL,20,Fschool is the heart of it and it's
OL,21,Ffantastic that we can give back".
